    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but what is the point of being \"strong\" if it just means enduring more agony? it feels less like strength and more like a prison sentence. i look at people who can just live, move, and exist without this weight, and it feels so unfair. sometimes i just think about how much easier it would be if everything was just... still. if the noise and the pain just stopped for good. like, wouldn't there be a certain kind of peace in just not having to fight anymore?",
